SHIGELLOSIS - TAIWAN: BACKGROUND
********************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
Date: Mon, 09 Nov 1998 21:04:11 -0800
From: "Stephen A. Berger, M.D." <mberger@post.tau.ac.il>

The following background data on shigellosis in Taiwan were
abstracted from the GIDEON software program:
Year Cases reported
1988 192
1990 141
1992 88
1993 207
1994 112
1995 562 *
1996 372 **
1997 500 ***
-------------------------
* 81.2% below age 14 years: 71.4% in Taoyuan County and 81.5% due
to _Shigella sonnei_.
** 253 of these confirmed; 51.2% below age 14 years and 15.2%
imported; 27.3% in Tauyuan County; 61.7% due to _S. flexneri_.
*** 401 confirmed - includes 15 imported cases.
....................................................jw
